                        <p class="mb-0">&copy; 2026 ForumHub. Tous droits r√©serv√©s.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 text-end">
                        <small>
                            <a href="#">Politique de confidentialit√©</a> ‚Ä¢ 
                            <a href="#">Mentions l√©gales</a>
